###  https://w3id.org/biodivrisK-onto#TNFDStrategyD
:TNFDStrategyD rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                        :DisclosureRequirement ;
               :definedBy :TNFD ;
               rdfs:comment "TNFD recommended disclosure Strategy D: disclose the locations of assets and/or activities in direct operations and, where possible, upstream and downstream value chains that meet the criteria for priority locations."@en ;
               rdfs:label "TNFD Strategy D"@en .


###  https://w3id.org/biodivrisK-onto#TropicalAndes
:TropicalAndes rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                        :Biome ;
               rdfs:comment "Biodiversity hotspot in the Andes mountains of Peru, Colombia, Ecuador and Bolivia. Under-sampled in GBIF: occurrence records biased towards roads and urban areas, with insufficient coverage of high-altitude species."@en ;
               rdfs:label "Tropical Andes Biome"@en .


